       He shakes his head solemnly.  "A joke good Blackstorm, 'twas only a 
joke.  You said you wished to speak privately, personal quarters seemed the 
obvious choice.  Now, if you don't mind, I really would like to get your questions 
answered before i get shot in the back again."  He sighs and collapses back 
against the wall again.
